c: 57
v: 13
t: "On that Day, the hypocrites, both men and women, will say to the faithful, \"Wait a while for us, so that we may have some of your light.\" They will be told, \"Turn back and look for a light elsewhere.\" A wall will then be raised between them. It will have a gate on the inside of which will be grace and mercy and on the outside of which will be punishment"